{"tid":2253614,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"中國社科院報告：香港城市綜合經濟競爭力排第二　仍遜於深圳","createTime":"2020-10-22T09:22:43.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-22T10:23:31.000Z","uid":39464,"like":10,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"c0f31744576725c651dcb3df7cdddce97b9cf32a","tid":2253614,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-22T09:22:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static01-proxy.hket.com/res/v3/image/content/2780000/2783712/2020_1024.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic01-proxy.hket.com%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2780000%2F2783712%2F2020_1024.png&h=e4ea863f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n中國社會科學院今天發布《中國城市競爭力第18次報告》，兩個主榜維持去年的格局，香港在城市綜合經濟競爭力指數裡排第二，遜於深圳；而可持續競爭力指數中，香港排名第一。<br />\n<br />\n中國社會科學院是與內地經濟日報社共同發布《中國城市競爭力第18次報告》。<br />\n<br />\n今年的報告除了構建綜合經濟競爭力指數、可持續競爭力指數外，同時又在兩項指標下，分別構建了5個分項競爭力指數，以對2020年中國兩岸四地291個城市進行多維度比較研究。<br />\n<br />\n可持續競爭力指數中 香港蟬聯第一<br />\n<br />\n報告顯示，2020年城市綜合經濟競爭力指數10強依次是：深圳、香港、上海、北京、廣州、蘇州、台北、南京、武漢和無錫。<br />\n<br />\n而2020年中國可持續競爭力指數10強依次是：香港、深圳、台北、上海、北京、廣州、蘇州、南京、青島和武漢。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://china.hket.com/article/2783712/%E7%A4%BE%E7%A7%91%E9%99%A2%E5%A0%B1%E5%91%8A%EF%BC%9A%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E5%9F%8E%E5%B8%82%E7%B6%9C%E5%90%88%E7%B6%93%E6%BF%9F%E7%AB%B6%E7%88%AD%E5%8A%9B%E6%8E%92%E7%AC%AC%E4%BA%8C%20%20%E4%BB%8D%E9%81%9C%E6%96%BC%E6%B7%B1%E5%9C%B3\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fchina.hket.com%2Farticle%2F2783712%2F%25E7%25A4%25BE%25E7%25A7%2591%25E9%2599%25A2%25E5%25A0%25B1%25E5%2591%258A%25EF%25BC%259A%25E9%25A6%2599%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E5%259F%258E%25E5%25B8%2582%25E7%25B6%259C%25E5%2590%2588%25E7%25B6%2593%25E6%25BF%259F%25E7%25AB%25B6%25E7%2588%25AD%25E5%258A%259B%25E6%258E%2592%25E7%25AC%25AC%25E4%25BA%258C%2520%2520%25E4%25BB%258D%25E9%2581%259C%25E6%2596%25BC%25E6%25B7%25B1%25E5%259C%25B3&d=mhl3ai6H9Odyk596tiaOPYkJ8G0wCzjK2GZdEgWvKr0%3D&h=a0539d6d\" target=\"_blank\">https://china.hket.com/article/2783712/%E7%A4%BE%E7%A7%91%E9%99%A2%E5%A0%B1%E5%91%8A%EF%BC%9A%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E5%9F%8E%E5%B8%82%E7%B6%9C%E5%90%88%E7%B6%93%E6%BF%9F%E7%AB%B6%E7%88%AD%E5%8A%9B%E6%8E%92%E7%AC%AC%E4%BA%8C%20%20%E4%BB%8D%E9%81%9C%E6%96%BC%E6%B7%B1%E5%9C%B3</a>"},{"pid":"46d86d306a441216262e366621636f6f2bb1a33b","tid":2253614,"uid":49784,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-22T09:23:42.000Z","msg":"得喇得喇，咁又點"},{"pid":"7493911b399e825d233f4eda5fc05e6ee117f983","tid":2253614,"uid":17641,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-22T09:23:45.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"xx-large\"><strong>深圳人民醫院萬歲</strong></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"679cb4c00c921131e4d31c9d7b26d49623b1410d","tid":2253614,"uid":60321,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-22T09:24:33.000Z","msg":"啲垃圾榜你話咩咪咩"},{"pid":"5dbfa6339520d6dbcb6cf5f7e7df50dbae92a983","tid":2253614,"uid":89608,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-22T09:24:42.000Z","msg":"叻啦, 終於成功啦"},{"pid":"b9de5c1dd57973c4251ae0467c0942faff2b8d5c","tid":2253614,"uid":32220,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-22T09:24:45.000Z","msg":"集到資先講野啦垃圾"},{"pid":"fa1f8cedb738fc94f1c0017b1b97f0db548023f8","tid":2253614,"uid":31744,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-22T09:25:09.000Z","msg":"台北表示：<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"55e4b840b513466366fc845ccb3f229df047ce27","tid":2253614,"uid":221343,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-22T09:25:10.000Z","msg":"台北又關你事？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5b3ab8440faf77a6511feea8ff2f5e75949149a5","tid":2253614,"uid":31744,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-22T09:25:40.000Z","msg":"台北都有，唔撚加埋新加坡？"},{"pid":"9b5917506f83e3793063c315cc1cf6ba9923a215","tid":2253614,"uid":13